title.narrative: Government Financial Management and Revenue Administration Project

description.narrative: In light of the more limited scope of GFMRAP after the recommended restructuring, the overall Project Development Objective is changed to the following: The objective of the Project is to improve efficiency, governance, integrity and transparency in the Borrower's public financial management. This adjustment scales down the ambition by focusing on public expenditure management and by not being the overarching reform umbrella envisioned in the Project Appraisal Document.
